kman>',1,'2017-01-01'),(297,'Off-Duty Alien','Citrus IPA','2018','Off-Duty Alien is a citrus IPA, brewed with blood orange and grapefruit to enhance the citurs characteristics of the hops.','https://images.punkapi.com/v2/keg.png',6.5,50,1010,1060,20,10,4.4,83,20,25,19,NULL,NULL,'John Jenkman <johnjenkman>',1,'2018-01-01'),(298,'East Of Vermont','Mango & Peach Milkshake Vermont IPA.','2018','A Vermont IPA with fruit and milk sugars added - recreating fruity milkshake character in an IPA.','https://images.punkapi.com/v2/keg.png',7.8,15,1018,1077,20,10,4.4,77,20,25,21,NULL,NULL,'John Jenkman <johnjenkman>',1,'2018-01-01'),(299,'Declassified Demi-God','Barrel-Aged Imperial Milk Stout.','2018','An exclusive barrel-aged blend, brought together to reward investors on Equity for Punks USA; two imperial stouts aged in grain whisky barrels for over a year.',NULL,14.1,70,1020,1127,90,46,4.1,84,20,25,21,NULL,NULL,'John Jenkman <johnjenkman>',6,'2018-01-01'),(300,'Raspberry Popsicle Parade','Raspberry Berliner Weisse.','2018','A draft-only kettle-soured raspberry ale, brewed to just 0.5% ABV, using our knowledge from brewing both Blitz and Nanny State. Aromas of fresh raspberry juice, soft red berries, and a blast of lemon zest, with a juicy palate encompassing zingy acidity and the smooth velvety note of oats, rounding out this low-ABV juicebox.','https://images.punkapi.com/v2/keg.png',0.5,8,1005,1009,8,4,3.5,44,20,25,21,NULL,NULL,'John Jenkman <johnjenkman>',1,'2018-01-01'),(301,'Indie Pale Ale','True Independent Craft.','2018','A non-dry-hopped pale ale, using new hopping technqiues and in- depth fermentation know-how.',NULL,4.2,30,1008,1044,16.6,8,4.6,82,20,25,21,NULL,NULL,'John Jenkman <johnjenkman>',1,'2018-01-01'),(302,'Small Batch: Dry-hopped Pilsner','Dry-hopped lager.','2018','A BrewDog bar exclusive draft lager, brewed with Weihenstephan\'s lager yeast, and dry-hopped with the contemporary German variety Saphir; this lager has been lightly centrifuged and packaged at 